Sentencas: When processed using state-of-the-art techniques, Solid Oxide Cells (SOCs) fabrication (e.g. tape casting) requires many steps.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: Recently, Additive Manufacturing (AM) techniques have gained popularity to complement or substitute SOCs fabrication processes.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: AM allows the combination of different techniques to produce complete cells, minimizing material waste while reducing the number of fabrication steps and improving their reliability.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: 3D printed symmetrical cells with composition LSM-YSZ/YSZ/LSM-YSZ were prepared by a robocasting and inkjet printing hybrid technology, followed by a co-sintering step.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: Printability tests and rheological characterization have been made on the robocast LSM-YSZ slurries for the electrodes and on the water-based YSZ ink for inkjet printing to produce the dense electrolyte.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: This study presents the fabrication of complete cells with self-standing robocast electrodes combined with inkjet printed electrolytes and their co-sintering in one step.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: After cosintering, the symmetrical cells were characterized by SEM-EDX, XRD and EIS.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: The microstructural analysis confirmed the feasibility of the process and its reproducibility.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: The electrochemical characterization led to an ASR value of approximate to 2.1 Omega cm(2) at 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting

Sentencas: These remarkable results demonstrate the potential of robocasting and inkjet printing for the fabrication of multi-material energy devices.
Titulo: Hybrid-3D printing of symmetric solid oxide cells by inkjet printing and robocasting
